    var lopList = "[fr-CA]";
    var isAutoTranslateToFrench = false;
    var languageOfPreference = "es-US";
    var isShadowModeEnabled = false;

    if (isShadowModeEnabled && isLoPToAutoTranslateAvailable()) {
        P.when('jQuery', 'ready').execute(function ($) {
            $('#translate-call-shadow-mode').click();
        });
    }
    if(isAutoTranslateToFrench) {
        // auto translation will be enabled based on cookie value. For 1 or undefined we auto translate and for others we show original
        // for more details refer: https://w.amazon.com/bin/view/NARX/Projects/FRCX-Customer-Reviews/
        var stickyCookieValue = document.cookie.match(/(?:(?:^|.*;\s*)cm-cr-sticky-translate\s*\=\s*([^;]*).*$)|^.*$/).pop();
        // Cookie value will be 1 when reviews are translated So checking if reviews are already translated on page load
        if (isLoPToAutoTranslateAvailable() && (stickyCookieValue === undefined || stickyCookieValue === "1")) {
            P.when('jQuery', 'ready', 'cr-generic-declarative-actions').execute(function ($) {
                $('#cr-translate--1237280010.cr-translate-these-reviews-section a').click();
            });
        }
    } else {
        if (document.cookie.replace(/(?:(?:^|.*;\s*)cm-cr-sticky-translate\s*\=\s*([^;]*).*$)|^.*$/, "$1")) {
            P.when('jQuery', 'ready', 'cr-generic-declarative-actions').execute(function ($) {
                $('#cr-translate--1237280010.cr-translate-these-reviews-section a').click();
            });
        }
    }

    function isLoPToAutoTranslateAvailable() {
        for(const lop of lopList.replace('[', '').replace(']', '').split(',')){
            if(lop.trim() === languageOfPreference) {
                return true;
            }
        }
        return false;
    }

    <span class="cr-original-review-content">50’ TV IS NOT 50INCH</span><span class="cr-translated-review-content aok-hidden"></span>
  
  
</a></div><span data-hook="review-date" class="a-size-base a-color-secondary review-date">Calificado en Estados Unidos el 8 de noviembre de 2023</span><div class="a-row a-spacing-mini review-data review-format-strip"><span data-hook="format-strip-linkless" class="a-color-secondary">Tamaño : 50 inches</span><i class="a-icon a-icon-text-separator" role="img" aria-label="|"></i><a class="a-link-normal" target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="/-/es/gp/help/customer/display.html/ref=cm_cr_dp_d_rvw_avp?nodeId=G75XTB7MBMBTXP6W"><span data-hook="avp-badge-linkless" class="a-size-mini a-color-state a-text-bold">Compra verificada</span></a></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-small review-data"><span data-hook="review-body" class="a-size-base review-text"><div data-a-expander-name="review_text_read_more" data-a-expander-collapsed-height="300" class="a-expander-collapsed-height a-row a-expander-container a-expander-partial-collapse-container" style="max-height:300px"><div data-hook="review-collapsed" aria-expanded="false" class="a-expander-content reviewText review-text-content a-expander-partial-collapse-content">







  
    <span class="cr-original-review-content">I bought the 50 inch version and measured my wall and the gap was exactly 50 inches so it would be perfectly flush against my wall. I had received the tv and once I had finished mounting it I noticed a huge gap. So I did what anyone else would do, I measured the tv. THE TV WAS 45 inches SMH. The box was 50 inches but the tv inside was 45. Everything else on the tv is perfect hence the reason I left 4 stars. But they should really put the actual size of the tv if it’s going to be 5 inches smaller because now I have a ugly gap on my wall.</span><span class="cr-translated-review-content aok-hidden"></span>

    <span class="cr-original-review-content">The TCL 75-Inch Class S4 4K LED Smart TV has completely transformed my home entertainment experience. This television, from the 2023 model lineup, offers an impressive array of features that deliver an exceptional viewing experience.<br><br>First and foremost, the 75-inch display is a showstopper. The 4K resolution and Dolby Vision HDR support result in stunningly clear and vibrant visuals. The audio quality is rich, detailed, and fills the room, making every scene come to life with depth and clarity.<br><br>Having Fire TV built right in is a game-changer. Accessing a wide range of streaming services, apps, and content has never been easier. Setting it up was straightforward, and the included user guide was helpful.<br><br>All in all, the TCL 75-Inch Class S4 4K LED Smart TV is a fantastic addition to any home. With its impressive display, powerful sound, and the convenience of Fire TV, it offers everything you need for a top-notch entertainment experience. It's a brilliant investment for those who crave both quality and convenience in their home theater setup.</span><span class="cr-translated-review-content aok-hidden"></span>

</a></div><span data-hook="review-date" class="a-size-base a-color-secondary review-date">Calificado en Estados Unidos el 25 de octubre de 2023</span><div class="a-row a-spacing-mini review-data review-format-strip"><span data-hook="format-strip-linkless" class="a-color-secondary">Tamaño : 65 inches</span><i class="a-icon a-icon-text-separator" role="img" aria-label="|"></i><a class="a-link-normal" target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="/-/es/gp/help/customer/display.html/ref=cm_cr_dp_d_rvw_avp?nodeId=G75XTB7MBMBTXP6W"><span data-hook="avp-badge-linkless" class="a-size-mini a-color-state a-text-bold">Compra verificada</span></a></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-small review-data"><span data-hook="review-body" class="a-size-base review-text"><div data-a-expander-name="review_text_read_more" data-a-expander-collapsed-height="300" class="a-expander-collapsed-height a-row a-expander-container a-expander-partial-collapse-container" style="max-height:300px"><div data-hook="review-collapsed" aria-expanded="false" class="a-expander-content reviewText review-text-content a-expander-partial-collapse-content">







  
    <span class="cr-original-review-content">I have had this 2 weeks now and I am pleased with this TV.  A 65" TV for under $380. is amazing for this quality.  I am not tech savey about bites and bits and pixals but I think the picture is very good.  The color is bright and clear.  The sound is also to my liking because I'm not adjusting it for every show.  We stream and have access to thousands of shows so the sound does need to be turned up or down sometimes. We do not  play games with it so I cannot comment on that feature.  It weighs almost 50 pounds so you will probably need a extra set of hands to move it safely.  I was worried I would be unhappy with it and the quality would be reflected by the price, but that has not been the case.  I am very satisfied with this TV.</span><span class="cr-translated-review-content aok-hidden"></span>

    <span class="cr-original-review-content">The TV works as intended. I can scroll on the screen but when I select a name nothing happens. The only way I'm able to fix this is by force stopping the app through the app managment in the TV settings.<br><br>Sometimes the YouTube app will crash during a video without warning.</span><span class="cr-translated-review-content aok-hidden"></span>

<div id="R2O62AWBMJLW63-review-card" class="a-row a-spacing-none"><div id="customer_review-R2O62AWBMJLW63" class="a-section celwidget" data-csa-c-id="5534cz-3l3lqm-7qc7p2-9vycff" data-cel-widget="customer_review-R2O62AWBMJLW63"><div data-hook="genome-widget" class="a-row a-spacing-mini"><a href="/-/es/gp/profile/amzn1.account.AFVWQJXVPDNFZS56WM3NOJQCCDSA/ref=cm_cr_dp_d_gw_tr?ie=UTF8" class="a-profile" data-a-size="small"><div aria-hidden="true" class="a-profile-avatar-wrapper"><div class="a-profile-avatar"><img src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/G/01/x-locale/common/grey-pixel.gif" class="a-lazy-loaded" data-src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/amazon-avatars-global/default._CR0,0,1024,1024_SX48_.png"><noscript><img src="https://images-na.ssl-images-amazon.com/images/S/amazon-avatars-global/default._CR0,0,1024,1024_SX48_.png"/></noscript></div></div><div class="a-profile-content"><span class="a-profile-name">Brad Mock</span></div></a></div><div class="a-row"><a data-hook="review-title" class="a-size-base a-link-normal review-title a-color-base review-title-content a-text-bold" href="/-/es/gp/customer-reviews/R2O62AWBMJLW63/ref=cm_cr_dp_d_rvw_ttl?ie=UTF8&amp;ASIN=B0C1HZW4L8"><i data-hook="review-star-rating" class="a-icon a-icon-star a-star-4 review-rating"><span class="a-icon-alt">4.0 de 5 estrellas</span></i><span class="a-letter-space"></span>







  
    <span class="cr-original-review-content">Great TV for the price but no 5G</span><span class="cr-translated-review-content aok-hidden"></span>
  
  
</a></div><span data-hook="review-date" class="a-size-base a-color-secondary review-date">Calificado en Estados Unidos el 1 de septiembre de 2023</span><div class="a-row a-spacing-mini review-data review-format-strip"><span data-hook="format-strip-linkless" class="a-color-secondary">Tamaño : 55 inches</span><i class="a-icon a-icon-text-separator" role="img" aria-label="|"></i><a class="a-link-normal" target="_blank" rel="noopener" href="/-/es/gp/help/customer/display.html/ref=cm_cr_dp_d_rvw_avp?nodeId=G75XTB7MBMBTXP6W"><span data-hook="avp-badge-linkless" class="a-size-mini a-color-state a-text-bold">Compra verificada</span></a></div><div class="a-row a-spacing-small review-data"><span data-hook="review-body" class="a-size-base review-text"><div data-a-expander-name="review_text_read_more" data-a-expander-collapsed-height="300" class="a-expander-collapsed-height a-row a-expander-container a-expander-partial-collapse-container" style="max-height:300px"><div data-hook="review-collapsed" aria-expanded="false" class="a-expander-content reviewText review-text-content a-expander-partial-collapse-content">







  
    <span class="cr-original-review-content">We bought this TV for our bedroom and the picture and features were all we have grown to expect from a TCL/Fire TV.  My only grouse is there is no 5G it seems, really a 2023 model TV with no 5G!!!  Because of this it took many hours to download and activate all the options we regularly use and at least one of our services often does not want to stream on 4G.  Dammit.<br><br>The Bluetooth feature was a selling point as I often watch TV late at night using headphones and bought an inexpensive sound bar with a subwoofer for those times we want better bigger sound.  Once these are paired anytime I turn on either device the TV automatically connects and disables the set speakers, very convenient.  The remote uses the same familiar Fire format so all the buttons are natural to fins, I really do like this.<br><br>Sound is important to me and the onboard speakers are about average, okay for casual viewing but not for music or louder movies and such.  The optical out worked on some apps but not on others namely Netflix so I have to connect our sound bar by Bluetooth which works but is not optimal.</span><span class="cr-translated-review-content aok-hidden"></span>

var cloudfrontImg = new Image();
var shouldExecuteOnload = ("1" == "1");
if (shouldExecuteOnload) {

      imageAssets.push("https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/checkout/assets/carrot._CB485936886_.gif");
      imageAssets.push("https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/checkout/thank-you-page/assets/yellow-rounded-corner-sprite._CB485934148_.gif");
      imageAssets.push("https://m.media-amazon.com/images/G/01/checkout/thank-you-page/assets/white-rounded-corner-sprite._CB485935362_.gif");

    // pre-fetching image assets
    for (var i=0; i<imageAssets.length; i++) {
       new Image().src = imageAssets[i];
    }
    // pre-fetching css and js assets based on different browser types
    var isIE = /*@cc_on!@*/0;
    var isFireFox = /Firefox/.test(navigator.userAgent);
    if (isIE) {
      for (var i=0; i<jsCssAssets.length; i++) {
        new Image().src = jsCssAssets[i];
      }
    }
    else if (isFireFox) {
      for (var i=0; i<jsCssAssets.length; i++) {
        var o =  document.createElement("object");
        o.data = jsCssAssets[i];
        o.width = o.height = 0;
        document.body.appendChild(o);
      }
    }
}

    var onload = function () {
        setTimeout(prefetchTYPAssets, 2000);
    };
    if (window.addEventListener) {
        window.addEventListener("load", onload);
    } else if (window.attachEvent) { /* for <= IE 8 */
        window.attachEvent("onload", onload);
    }
</script>

  <script type="text/javascript">(function ($Nav) {
"use strict";

if (typeof $Nav === 'undefined' || $Nav === null || typeof $Nav.when !== 'function') {
    return;
}

$Nav.when('$', 'data', 'flyout.yourAccount', 'sidepanel.csYourAccount',
          'config')
    .run("BuyitAgain-YourAccount-SidePanel",
    function ($, data, yaFlyout, csYourAccount, config) {
        if (config.disableBuyItAgain) {
            return;
        }
        var render = function (data) {
            if (data.dramResult) {
                var widgetHtml = data.dramResult;
                navbar.sidePanel({
                    flyoutName: 'yourAccount',
                    data: {html: widgetHtml}
                });
            }
        };

        var renderBuyItAgain = function (biaData) {
            if (csYourAccount) {
                csYourAccount.register(render, biaData);
            } else {
                render(biaData);
            }
        };

        var truncateAndRestructureYaFlyout = function() {
            if (window.P) {
                P.when('A', 'a-truncate').execute(function(A, truncate) {
                    var truncateElements = A.$('.a-truncate');
                    A.each(truncateElements, function(element) {
                        truncate.get(element).update();
                    });
                    var recommendationsWidget = document.getElementById('bia-hcb-widget');
                    if (recommendationsWidget) { 
                        var navFlyout = recommendationsWidget.parentElement;
                        var navFlyoutPaddingBottom = parseInt(window.getComputedStyle(navFlyout).getPropertyValue('padding-bottom'));
                        var navFlyoutContentHeight = navFlyout.clientHeight - navFlyoutPaddingBottom;
                        while (recommendationsWidget.offsetHeight > navFlyoutContentHeight && recommendationsWidget.offsetHeight > 0){
                            var recommendations = recommendationsWidget.querySelectorAll('.biaNavFlyoutFaceout');
                            if (recommendations.length <= 1) {
                                break;
                            }
                            var lastRecommendation = recommendations[recommendations.length - 1];
                            lastRecommendation.parentElement.removeChild(lastRecommendation);
                        }
                    }
               });
            }
        };

        yaFlyout.sidePanel.onData(truncateAndRestructureYaFlyout);
        yaFlyout.onShow(truncateAndRestructureYaFlyout);

    yaFlyout.onRender(function() {
            $.ajax({
                url: '/gp/bia/external/bia-hcb-ajax-handler.html',
                data: {"biaHcbRid":"44ZATTTE1GAE42AQ9YCT"},
                dataType: 'json',
                timeout: 4*1000,
                success: renderBuyItAgain,
                error: function (jqXHR, textStatus, errorThrown) {
                }
            });
        });
    });
})(window.$Nav);</script>
